HEADWORD: Cannibalism
<hw>Can"ni*bal*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>cannibalisme</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act or practice of eating human
